        "para_1": "Kansawala is India’s foremost handcrafted metal utensil brand — a four-generation family business founded in 1945 by Sh. Mukundray Fulchand in Sihor, Bhavnagar, Gujarat. For over 75 years, we have been handcrafting pure Kansa (Bronze), Brass (Pital) and Copper (Tamba) utensils using traditional techniques passed down through generations of the Mukundray Fulchand family.",
